1. Ja *otvaram* prozor da udje svež vazduh. (I'm opening the window to let in fresh air.)
2. Oni *otvaraju* novu radnju u centru grada. (They're opening a new store in the city center.)
3. Kada se *otvori* novi restoran, idemo zajedno da probamo hranu. (When the new restaurant opens, let's go together to try the food.)
4. *Otvori* mi vrata, molim te. (Open the door for me, please.)
5. Da li možeš da *otvoriš* ovu teglu? Mnogo je zategnuta. (Can you open this jar? It's really tight.)
6. Jutros sam *otvorila* svoj mail i videla puno novih poruka. (This morning I opened my email and saw a lot of new messages.)
7. Ona se nada da će se njena situacija uskoro *otvoriti*. (She hopes that her situation will soon improve.)
8. Kada *otvoriš* ovaj dokument, pogledaj prvu stranu. (When you open this document, look at the first page.)
9. Danas je lep dan, trebalo bi da *otvorimo* prozore i pustimo sunce da uđe. (Today is a beautiful day, we should open the windows and let the sun in.)
10. Kada se *otvaraju* prijave za konkurs? (When do the applications for the competition open?)